{"tid":677205,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果拒絕Steam Link流式盒應用上架App Store","createTime":"2018-05-25T03:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T04:50:33.000Z","uid":12599,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9c796beb69ed67ac8126d62e8f7f0c028cb296ff","tid":677205,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"Valve已經在谷歌Play商店中上線Steam Link應用，Steam 流式盒應用可將電腦桌面遊戲發送到安卓/iOS設備，通過藍牙控制器或者Steam控制器暢玩PC/Mac端上Steam庫中的遊戲。不過這一計劃似乎遭遇了小挫折，外媒表示蘋果已經拒絕了Steam Link流式盒應用上架蘋果的App Store平台，理由是存在&quot;業務衝突&quot;Valve表示，蘋果公司將&ldquo;與應用程序準則的業務衝突&rdquo;作為撤銷批准的理由。而在5月7日，蘋果最初已經批准了Steam Link應用的上架請求，但在之後蘋果以&ldquo;業務衝突&rdquo;撤銷了其上架，並解釋稱原來的審核團隊並未意識到應用的違規。 Valve 申訴道Steam Link應用式基於局域網的遠程桌面程式，而且指出了App Store中現有的許多類似應用，但此申訴並未被蘋果接受。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://9to5mac.com/2018/05/24/steam-link-for-ios-rejected/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2Fsteam-link-for-ios-rejected%2F&d=sETKHKOC8XK5OnScn6%2Bzn8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=e564df1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://9to5mac.com/2018/05/24/steam-link-for-ios-rejected/</a><br />\n<br />\n留名睇bam堆nvidia shield streaming<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a287b46085998a17f3b76cd96f7c20caf01f7b","tid":677205,"uid":42453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:17:37.000Z","msg":"Apple自掘墳墓 <br />\n好搞唔搞 去搞steam"},{"pid":"f547db5e522e65e2b9291656a0db173acc605008","tid":677205,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:19:54.000Z","msg":"等睇世界大戰"},{"pid":"f43deb09e574032875dfba16ecbc4402098f3d27","tid":677205,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"唔關我事"},{"pid":"9d974ec44fa8288153a6794e74e2061ea66e7451","tid":677205,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite